name: 雷斯·丹尼尔
introduction: The Founder of Threes a Crowd Management & Productions Also known for Sky Ones: Ocean Rescue, Sky Kids Dive in and do it & 4 time best supporting actor nominee for his part in The Flytipper & Trumped movies.Since playing Mowgli in the Jungle Book national tour and Sammy David Jnr in The Rat Pack show international tour, Reis has moved into the world of Tv , Film and stand up comedy. Guest appearing in channel 4s sketch comedy show Pop Sludge and working with online channels such as , Uni lad , Ladbible , Dream Team F.C. and the Entertainer Squad.Reis has Several films and a Tv series being released in 2019.
